; Loaded via includeIf in ~/.gitconfig only when the current repo's
; gitdir contains "github.com/" (e.g. ~/Developer/github.com/<owner>/<repo>).
; Overrides user.email to the GitHub noreply so personal email is never
; leaked to public github commits.

